Website features
=======
* Real time poll for discussion questions
* Mobile support

Slides
=======
* Benefits and dangers slide
    - Benefits/dangers slide
        - Add a real time poll (displayed on the next slide)
        - For now, have preset answer distribution
        - But add the infrastructure to let different website users vote
    - Why we're learning about it slide
        - Visual examples of...
            * Fake articles/images
            * Why it's a useful tool
                - Coding/making software
            * But emphasize that it can be wrong
* Diffusion process slide
    - Better animations for the diffusion process
        - Linear diffusion process (image on one side, noise on the other)
        - Make it interactable
            * Slider to manipulate the amount of noise
* CLIP slide
    - Illustration of embedding mapping from text/images to 2D embedding space
    - Interactive demo
        - Select different points on the graph
        - Produce different image/text pairs 
        - Do this assigning image/text pairs to a point, finding the nearest neighbor when selecting a new point

